General.Name: Auriant Mining AB (publ)
General.Description: Auriant Mining AB (publ), a junior mining company, engages in the exploration and production of gold in Russia. The company was formerly known as Central Asia Gold AB and changed its name to Auriant Mining AB (publ) in June 2012. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. Auriant Mining AB (publ) operates as a subsidiary of Bertil Holdings Ltd.
